### Get Settings (Surcharge + Receptionist Count)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/settings

### Update Surcharge Settings
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/settings/surcharge
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "foreignGuest": 1.5,
  "extraPerson": 1.5,
  "holiday": 2.0
}

